org.kitesdk.minicluster

Class MiniCluster

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.kitesdk.minicluster.MiniCluster

  • public class MiniCluster
extends Object
    A in process MiniCluster implementation for Kite that is configurable with Services that make up the MiniCluster. Examples of Services are HDFS, HBase, Zookeeper, etc... This MiniCluster should be built with its internal Builder class, which will validate proper configuration of the MiniCluster. For example, a Service can have dependencies, so the builder will validate that proper Service dependencies have been added to the MiniCluster.
